{
  "texts": [
    "All constructs had outer loadings exceeding 0.7 (Hair et al., 2019).",
    "The composite reliability and average variance were found to be higher than 0.7 and 0.5, respectively (Usakli & Kucukergin, 2018; Fornell & Larcker, 1981).",
    "Further, Cronbach's alpha values were higher than 0.7 (Hair et al., 2017).",
    "Based on these criteria, cognitive validity was established.",
    "Fornell and Larcker (1981) proposed the method used in this study to assess discriminant validity."
  ]
}